## 3) Agenda Specification (Validation Rules)

### 3.1 DAY_ROLE_ENUM (mandatory, exactly 1 per day)
Allowed values:
- REST
- RECOVERY
- ENDURANCE
- QUALITY
- OPTIONAL
- FLEX
- TRAVEL
- EVENT
- OFF_BIKE

### 3.2 INTENSITY_DOMAIN_ENUM (optional, max 1; default = NONE)
Allowed values:
- NONE
- RECOVERY
- ENDURANCE
- TEMPO
- SST
- VO2MAX

### 3.3 LOAD_MODALITY_ENUM (optional, max 1; default = NONE)
Allowed values:
- NONE
- K3

### 3.4 Combination Rules (Strict)
Base rules:
- DAY_ROLE is mandatory.
- INTENSITY_DOMAIN defaults to NONE.
- LOAD_MODALITY defaults to NONE.
- No durations, no zones (Z1-Z7), no %FTP, no intervals, no kJ/TSS in agendas.

Allowed combinations:
- REST -> INTENSITY_DOMAIN=NONE, LOAD_MODALITY=NONE
- OFF_BIKE -> INTENSITY_DOMAIN=NONE, LOAD_MODALITY=NONE
- TRAVEL -> INTENSITY_DOMAIN=NONE, LOAD_MODALITY=NONE
- FLEX -> INTENSITY_DOMAIN=NONE, LOAD_MODALITY=NONE
- RECOVERY -> INTENSITY_DOMAIN in {NONE, RECOVERY}, LOAD_MODALITY=NONE
- ENDURANCE -> INTENSITY_DOMAIN in {NONE, ENDURANCE}, LOAD_MODALITY=NONE
- OPTIONAL -> INTENSITY_DOMAIN in {NONE, ENDURANCE}, LOAD_MODALITY=NONE
- QUALITY -> INTENSITY_DOMAIN in {TEMPO, SST, VO2MAX}, LOAD_MODALITY in {NONE, K3}
- EVENT -> INTENSITY_DOMAIN in {ENDURANCE, TEMPO, SST, VO2MAX}, LOAD_MODALITY in {NONE, K3}

Forbidden combinations (examples):
- ENDURANCE + SST / VO2MAX
- RECOVERY + SST / VO2MAX
- QUALITY + NONE
- QUALITY + ENDURANCE / RECOVERY
- Any DAY_ROLE + (zones, durations, %FTP, interval notation)
- LOAD_MODALITY=K3 with INTENSITY_DOMAIN=VO2MAX (for this preview layer)

